sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as /api/budgets/{id}
    participant Auth
    participant Db as FinancetrackerContext

    Client->>API: GET /api/budgets/{id}
    API->>Auth: validate token -> get userId
    Auth-->>API: userId
    API->>Db: SELECT budget WHERE BudgetId==id AND UserId==userId INCLUDE Category
    Db-->>API: budget or null
    API-->>Client: 200 OK { budget } or 404
